4
00:00:07,507 --> 00:00:08,976
<i>With the arrival of...</i>

5
00:00:08,976 --> 00:00:11,612
<i>Hang on! Can't we just skip</i>
<i>this narration already?</i>

6
00:00:11,612 --> 00:00:12,980
