15
00:02:05,058 --> 00:02:08,395
We looked for him everywhere,
but we couldn't find him.

16
00:02:08,829 --> 00:02:11,498
It appears that he is no longer
on these grounds.

17
00:02:13,433 --> 00:02:15,202
Are you joking?

18
00:02:17,337 --> 00:02:18,238
But, chief!

19
00:02:18,739 --> 00:02:21,241
Do you think "we couldn't find him"
is going to cut it?

20
00:02:21,241 --> 00:02:22,342
But... but we...

21
00:02:22,342 --> 00:02:24,511
I don't need your back talk,
Hasegawa.

22
00:02:24,511 --> 00:02:26,747
You Edo officials
have just one job,

23
