a rich old hag or two?

46
00:03:28,875 --> 00:03:30,677
Man up and grow a pair,
mop top!

47
00:03:30,677 --> 00:03:33,580
All you ever care about
is money, money, money.

48
00:03:33,580 --> 00:03:35,082
How petty are you?

49
