the smelly breath of old guys.

65
00:04:14,387 --> 00:04:16,123
‐Shinpachi?
‐Yes?

66
00:04:16,123 --> 00:04:18,091
You don't have a girlfriend
at all, do you?

67
00:04:18,091 --> 00:04:19,926
What's this, all of a sudden?

68
00:04:19,926 --> 00:04:22,262
Are you interested in going out
with an older woman at all?

69
