What do you take me for?

71
00:04:29,936 --> 00:04:32,072
I'm a young man
in the prime of my youth!

72
00:04:32,072 --> 00:04:33,874
Don't get your panties
bunched up, man.

73
00:04:33,874 --> 00:04:34,741
The thing about money,

74
